#: ../../../prop_sf/COMPILE_FLAGS.rst:2
msgid "COMPILE_FLAGS"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../prop_sf/COMPILE_FLAGS.rst:4
msgid "Additional flags to be added when compiling this source file."
msgstr "編譯此來源檔案時要新增的額外旗標。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/COMPILE_FLAGS.rst:6
msgid ""
"The ``COMPILE_FLAGS`` property, managed as a string, sets additional "
"compiler flags used that will be added to the list of compile flags when "
"this source file builds.  The flags will be added after target-wide flags."
msgstr ""
"以字串管理的 ``COMPILE_FLAGS`` 屬性，用於設定在建置此來源檔案時將新增到編譯旗"
"標清單中的額外編譯器旗標。這些旗標將在目標範圍的旗標之後新增。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/COMPILE_FLAGS.rst:10
msgid ""
"Use :prop_sf:`COMPILE_DEFINITIONS` to pass additional preprocessor "
"definitions."
msgstr "使用 :prop_sf:`COMPILE_DEFINITIONS` 傳遞額外的預處理器定義。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/COMPILE_FLAGS.rst:12
msgid ""
"Contents of ``COMPILE_FLAGS`` may use \"generator expressions\" with the "
"syntax ``$<...>``.  See the :manual:`cmake-generator-expressions(7)` manual "
"for available expressions.  However, :generator:`Xcode` does not support per-"
"config per-source settings, so expressions that depend on the build "
"configuration are not allowed with that generator."
msgstr ""
"``COMPILE_FLAGS`` 的內容可以使用語法 ``$<...>`` 的「生成器表達式」。請參閱 :"
"manual:`cmake-generator-expressions(7)` 手冊以了解可用的表達式。但是，:"
"generator:`Xcode` 不支援依組態和依來源的設定，因此不允許在該生成器中使用依賴"
"於建置組態的表達式。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/COMPILE_FLAGS.rst:21
msgid ""
"This property has been superseded by the :prop_sf:`COMPILE_OPTIONS` property."
msgstr "此屬性已被 :prop_sf:`COMPILE_OPTIONS` 屬性取代。"
